      "comment": "MY PADDY BOY (1) jumped from a squeeze box last start but was quickly into stride and led throughout to score (22.52) at this track in a Novice race over 400m. Great chance to get the job done again. YOUR MATE BOB (7) was on speed throughout but collided in the run and finished second (22.69) at this track over 400m in a Grade 5. Harder here but expected to measure up. POTENT CREW (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 400m behind Maximum Hughes (23.11) in a Grade 5. Has ability and is one of the better chances. CANYA BYPASS (8) is worth some thought after placing in an impressive time last start.",
